\newlabel{fig:ex43-violins-multi}{{4.6}{30}{Required number of candidates and voters to remove, to transform a TVCR profile into a CR or a VR one, from Experiment 3. The plot is structured in the same way as in Figure \ref {fig:ex43-violins}, except one difference. Split in half violins no longer represent independent deletion of the candidates or the voters, but correspond to simultaneous deletion of both. If there is no violin (horizontal line), it means that all the values were identical. \relax }{figure.caption.24}{}}
